714989f-a.text:
West 106th Street, north side, west from Manhattan, to and across Columbus Avenues. The block front consists of structures numbered 49-51 (right) to 71 (left, corner building). The Ninth Avenue "El" which runs on Columbus Avenue at this point is obscured
by the canopy at the left.
September 1934
George L. Balgue
